un faster than the mobs so that you can get ahead to cast.  BoF is NOT needed - jboots speed and no snare works for most mobs. <p><br>Aniar Orrenson<br>Wizard of the 33rd Season<br>Guild Leader of Nightwatch of Norrath<br>"You look up overkill in the dictionary and there's a picture of Aniar lol" Lotta on Saryrn<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27902" target="_blank">Look down my pants with Magelo!</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uellocopato.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ellocopato</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Channeler</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/26/01 10:31:04 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=248.topic&index=4>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: When can you first start Quad Kiting?</span><hr size=1> I was under the impression you coudl kite in your teens in the karanas with the slow speed of the bugs.  I never tried it, but that was my understanding.<br><br> <p><img src="http://members.home.net/ta-prexus/sigs/ellosig.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uaniar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aniar</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.docsmooth.com/images/dot.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/26/01 11:45:49 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=248.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.doc